Alacritty's config is parsed in a whole-file-first manner, meaning that if the
main alacritty.yml was the git tracked global one, local overrides would be
impossible. Instead, alacritty.yml is the local one and it needs to import the
global one explicitly.


On Windows, you need to

touch /mnt/c/Users/eatnu/AppData/Roaming/Alacritty/alacritty.yml

in order to enact changes in live terminals.
